ww.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sam-fender-ali-tant-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sam-fender-ali-tant-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sam-fender-ali-tant-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sam-fender-ali-tant-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sam-fender-ali-tant-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）</a>以他的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019">《 People Watch》（People Watch）</a>袭击了英国专辑排行榜的顶部，这是自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯</a>（Harry Styles）“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/harry-styles-new-album-harrys-house-3226209">哈利的房子</a>”以来，英国最大的开幕周。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019">Sam Fender  - “观看人物”专辑评论：反射性和敏锐的独立摇滚，来自North Shields的Shining Star</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<em><a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/">官方排行榜</a></em>，Fender在他的第三张专辑的开幕周中转移了107,100张图表单元，这是他连续第三张专辑。这也是他有史以来最大的开幕周，比2019年首次亮相“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sam-fender-hypersonic-missiles-review-2546624">Hypersonic导弹</a>”和2021年的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">十七岁</a>”的销售单位更多。</p><p>此外，这也是2025年最大的开幕周，也是英国最大的英国艺术家开幕周，因为Styles在三年前就获得了113,000个单位。</p><p>在这个十年的一周中，只有九位艺术家在一周内管理了100,000张英国专辑的销售 -<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>（Taylor Swift），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔（Adele）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">科尔（Coldplay）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran），哈里·斯泰尔斯</a>（Harry Sheeran），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈里·斯泰尔斯（Harry Styles）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">拿那个</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">阿巴（Abba）</a>和北极猴子（Abba）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">北极猴子</a>。</p><p>此外，“观看者”已成为本世纪英国表演最快的乙烯基专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3812392" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812392" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812392" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）“观看”专辑插图。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Sam-Fender-People-Watching-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3812392" class="wp-caption-text">山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）“观看”专辑插图。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>“这完全是压倒性的。感谢所有支持我们并在本周收听专辑的人。” Fender回答新闻。</p><p>本周早些时候，据报道，“观看的人” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-currently-outselling-rest-of-uk-top-10-combined-people-watching-3840843">正在当然可以卖空英国前十名中的其余总和</a>。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对“观看者”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019">四星级评论</a>中写道：“反思性，分析性和脆弱性，“观看的人”确实做了标题可能所暗示的：盘点使Fender成为他今天的人的角色，朋友和亲人。当他回顾迄今为止的生活时，他以敏感的方式接近每条曲目，甚至有罪恶感，也要考虑下一个可能是谁。”</p><p>在其他山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）新闻中，这位音乐家最近嘲笑了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-continues-to-tease-another-new-album-says-hes-desperate-to-make-a-punk-album-3840765">另一张新专辑，他说他“拼命”倾向于朋克风格的声音</a>。</p><p>在最近关于Apple Music 1的<em>The Zane Lowe节目</em>的采访中，Geordie词曲作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-planning-next-album-ive-got-a-load-of-new-songs-already-3839928">开放了有关与毒品战争的亚当·格兰迪尔（Adam Granduciel）合作的工作，并重申他已经在进行了后续工作</a>。</p><p> Fender最近在夏季<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-huge-summer-2025-uk-stadium-shows-buy-tickets-3814931">即将举行的英国体育场巡回演出</a>中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-more-huge-uk-outdoor-shows-for-summer-2025-3837652">增加了日期</a>- 包括曼彻斯特的Wythenshawe Park，Edinburgh Summer Sessions和贝尔法斯特的Boucher Road竞争地。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsam-fender-tickets%2Fartist%2F5242347" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-more-huge-uk-outdoor-shows-for-summer-2025-3837652">在此处</a>找到英国巡回演出的清单。</p><p>他还在下个月的仪式上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">获得了两项英国奖项的提名</a>：年度艺术家和Alt/Rock Act，并已宣布为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announced-as-record-store-day-uk-official-ambassador-3834386">唱片店Day UK 2025的正式大使。</a>该活动将于4月12日举行，Fender将在庆祝EP的一部分中发行两首新歌。</p><p>最重要的是，最近宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-raye-and-more-to-headline-2025-f1-british-grand-prix-3839703">Fender将是今年一级方程式英国大奖赛的头条新闻之一。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fenders-people-watching-earns-biggest-uk-opening-week-for-british-act-since-harry-styles-harrys-house-3842384">自哈里·斯泰尔斯（Harry Styles）“哈利的家”（Harry&#39;s House）以来，萨姆·芬德（Sam Fender）的“观看者”（Post Sam Fender）的“观看者”为英国的开幕周提供了最大</a>的开幕<a href="https://www.nme.com">周</a>。</p> ;
